---
// Who We Are — reference/html/index.html, section.who-section.
// Reference has NO h2 here; only "Who we are" eyebrow, 3 body paragraphs,
// and Mission/Vision cards. Copy extracted verbatim.
---
<section id="who-we-are" class="bg-[color:var(--color-bg-elevated)] py-24 md:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6">
    <p class="mb-6 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[color:var(--color-accent)]">
      Who we are
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-[color:var(--color-fg-subtle)] md:text-xl md:leading-[1.6]">
      <p>
        RxMedia was founded in 2018 with a clear purpose: to bridge addiction
        treatment centers and patients through digital advertising.
      </p>
      <p>
        Individuals seeking help often have trouble finding high-quality care,
        and even the best treatment centers can go unnoticed by those who need
        them the most. This disconnect fuels our desire to bring rehab centers
        a step closer to patients. Our approach? Providing digital marketing of
        the best caliber at an affordable cost.
      </p>
      <p>
        Even as we expand into new verticals, such as mental health and other
        healthcare providers, our core goal remains the same, and that is to
        ensure everyone finds the help they need.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[color:var(--color-border)] bg-[color:var(--color-bg)] p-8">
        <p class="mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[color:var(--color-accent)]">
          Our Mission
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold leading-snug md:text-2xl">
          To empower health and wellness brands through results-driven, ethical,
          and innovative digital marketing.
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[color:var(--color-border)] bg-[color:var(--color-bg)] p-8">
        <p class="mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[color:var(--color-accent-alt)]">
          Our Vision
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold leading-snug md:text-2xl">
          To be the go-to growth partner for organizations that are changing
          lives.
        </h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
